[b]Base: Final Devolution 2.7.1[/b]
Website being developed by Infinity Zr. http://img690.imageshack.us/img690/7199/75216301.png Sorry for no img tags. ^^
[IMG]http://i35.tinypic.com/bfkhmd.png[/img] [b][font=Orange]PlayerKilling[/font][/b]
Timers are based off of RuneScape, and are near-perfect. All PvP items are now added, the specials are being worked on to make them near-perfect. The skulling system works like it should, and every PvP code is re-written to it's top level. (As to my standards, at least) No overpowered items, un-real custom items, and nothing of that stuff. PlayerKilling/PvP is really, really, great.
